<myopenmath xmlns:pi="http://pretextbook.org/2020/pretext/internal" id="1455393">
<statement>
<p>
Suppose you want to make weekly deposits into an annuity. How often should interest be compounded for this account?</p>
<p><ol style="list-style-type:upper-alpha"><li>Annually</li> 
<li>Quarterly</li> 
<li>Daily</li> 
<li>Weekly</li> 
<li>Monthly</li> 
<li>Semi-annually</li> 
<li>It doesn't matter</li> 
</ol></p>


</statement>
<answer>
<p><ul><li>D: Weekly</li></ul></p>
</answer>

</myopenmath>